---
title: Caribbean Chickpea & Veggie Pie with Potato Mash Topping
description: And now for something completely different, meet our game-changing plant-based pie! A coconutty, Caribbean-spiced chickpea
filling meets a golden potato topping for a dish that's equally wholesome and delish.

